=== 伊拉克和沙姆伊斯蘭國 ===
2013年4月，[[巴格达迪|巴格达迪]]单方面宣布将“伊拉克伊斯兰国”和“努斯拉阵线”合并成一个组织“伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国”（{{lang-ar|الدولة الاسلامية في العراق والشام}} ''{{transl|ar|DIN|ad-Dawlat al-Islāmiyya fī’l-‘Irāq wa’sh-Shām}}''"，<u>Islamic State in Iraq and al-Sham</u>"，简称<u>ISIS</u>），又譯“伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯兰国”（"<u>Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant</u>"，简称<u>ISIL</u>）<ref>{{cite news|title=Key Free Syria Army rebel 'killed by Islamist group'|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-23283079|publisher=BBC|date=2013-07-12|access-date=2014-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125211923/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-23283079|archive-date=2015-11-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AlArabiya_9-4-2013">{{cite news |title=Al-Qaeda in Iraq confirms Syria's Nusra Front is part of its network |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/09/Al-Qaeda-in-Iraq-confirms-Syria-s-Nusra-Front-is-part-of-its-network.html |accessdate=2014-06-15 |agency=[[Al_Arabiya|Al Arabiya]] |date=2013-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119055306/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2013/04/09/Al-Qaeda-in-Iraq-confirms-Syria-s-Nusra-Front-is-part-of-its-network.html |archive-date=2016-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。两种不同的译名产生是由于对于叙利亚及周边地区，[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯人]]使用“''Shām''”（或''Shaam''，译为[[沙姆地区|沙姆地区]]），而[[欧美|欧美]]对相近的地理概念惯用“[[黎凡特|黎凡特]]”一词。不過在叙利亚的原“努斯拉阵线”成员不同意巴格达迪單方面宣佈「合并」的決定，兩者最終決裂。

2014年2月，在历经了8個月的权力争斗之后，蓋達组织宣布「伊拉克和沙姆伊斯蘭國」过于极端、殘忍、野蠻，而切斷了与它的所有联系。[[賓·拉登|賓·拉登]]的高級幕僚曾在21頁信函中，譴責該組織的惡行：包括多次炸毀[[清真寺|清真寺]]、违背《[[古蘭經|古蘭經]]》教義展开血腥[[種族清洗|種族清洗]]、使用[[氯氣|氯氣]]进行毒殺、在[[巴格達|巴格達]]的[[天主教堂|天主教堂]]裏[[屠殺|屠殺]]信徒，蓋達组织應與其[[劃清界限|劃清界限]]，以免形象被拖累<ref>{{cite web|last1=Barrett|first1=Kevin|script-title=en:ISIS “too extreme for al-Qaeda”|url=http://www.presstv.com/detail/2014/02/07/349703/isis-too-extreme-for-alqaeda/|website=www.presstv.com|publisher=[[Press_TV|PRESSTV]]|accessdate=2014-06-20|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140716222005/http://www.presstv.com/detail/2014/02/07/349703/isis%2Dtoo%2Dextreme%2Dfor%2Dalqaeda/|archivedate=2014-07-16}}</ref><ref name=AlQaedaTiesEnd>{{Cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/al-qaeda-disavows-any-ties-with-radical-islamist-isis-group-in-syria-iraq/2014/02/03/2c9afc3a-8cef-11e3-98ab-fe5228217bd1_story.html|title=Al-Qaeda disavows any ties with radical Islamist ISIS group in Syria, Iraq|work=The Washington Post|author=Liz Sly|date=2014-02-03|accessdate=2014-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170902133658/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/al-qaeda-disavows-any-ties-with-radical-islamist-isis-group-in-syria-iraq/2014/02/03/2c9afc3a-8cef-11e3-98ab-fe5228217bd1_story.html|archive-date=2017-09-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1078429|title=伊斯蘭國手段偏激 賓拉丹也切割 - 國際 - 自由時報電子報|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813000644/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1078429|archivedate=2014-08-13|accessdate=2014-08-18}}</ref>，故该组织已不被[[蓋達组织|蓋達组织]]所承认<ref name="bbc611">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-24179084 |title=Profile: Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant (ISIS) |publisher=BBC |date=2014-06-11 |access-date=2014-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920062525/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-24179084 |archive-date=2014-09-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过在[[歐巴馬|歐巴馬]]向伊拉克猛增军事行動之后，伊斯蘭國与伊拉克的蓋達組織又开始合作對抗[[美军|美军]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/yzyd/mil/20141114/c_1113250107.htm |title=“伊斯兰国”与“基地”达成协议共同对抗美军 |publisher=新华网 |accessdate=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129043510/http://news.xinhuanet.com/yzyd/mil/20141114/c_1113250107.htm |archive-date=2014-11-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 伊斯蘭國 ===
2014年6月29日，巴格达迪宣布將「伊拉克和沙姆」字樣捨去，直稱“伊斯兰国”（The Islamic State，簡稱：IS），巴格达迪恢復本名「易卜拉欣」，自稱[[哈里發|哈里發]]<ref>{{Cite news|title=全球最富恐怖组织ISIS宣布建立伊斯兰国|url=http://world.haiwainet.cn/n/2014/0630/c232591-20799037.html|work=海外网|date=2014-06-30|access-date=2014-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140724064150/http://world.haiwainet.cn/n/2014/0630/c232591-20799037.html|archive-date=2014-07-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=伊叛军宣布“建国” 头目自称全球穆斯林领袖|url=http://world.people.com.cn/n/2014/0630/c1002-25215787.html|work=人民网|date=2014-06-30|access-date=2014-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915045318/http://world.people.com.cn/n/2014/0630/c1002-25215787.html|archive-date=2014-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[阿拉伯世界|阿拉伯世界]]各國政府和反對該組織的人，用[[阿拉伯語|阿拉伯語]]的[[縮寫|縮寫]]Daʿesh（{{rtl-lang|ar|داعش}}，中文音译为“达伊沙”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forvo.com/word/%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%B4/#ar|title=داعش pronunciation: How to pronounce داعش in Arabic, Persian|first=Forvo|last=Team|publisher=|access-date=2014-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141124102028/http://www.forvo.com/word/%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%B4/#ar|archive-date=2014-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://world.people.com.cn/n/2014/1120/c1002-26063232.html |title=西班牙政府呼吁各国媒体和政府应将恐怖组织“伊斯兰国”改称“达伊沙” |publisher=人民网 |accessdate=2014-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213112727/http://world.people.com.cn/n/2014/1120/c1002-26063232.html |archive-date=2014-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）稱呼該組織，取其阿拉伯名的首個字母Dāl, ʾAlif, ʿAyn, Šīn組成<ref name="daesh3">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-27994277|title=Isis, Isil or Da'ish? What to call militants in Iraq|date=2014-06-24|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2014-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815130915/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-27994277|archive-date=2014-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該組織視這名稱為侮辱，因為名稱中沒有「伊斯蘭」一詞<ref name="daeshleparisien">{{cite web|url = http://www.leparisien.fr/international/daesh-isis-comment-doit-on-appeler-les-jihadistes-de-l-etat-islamique-15-09-2014-4136787.php|date = 2014-09-15|publisher = Le Parisien|title = Daesh, Isis...comment doit-on appeler les jihadistes de l'Etat islamique ?|accessdate = 2014-09-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140916082206/http://www.leparisien.fr/international/daesh-isis-comment-doit-on-appeler-les-jihadistes-de-l-etat-islamique-15-09-2014-4136787.php|archive-date = 2014-09-16|dead-url = no}}</ref>。有[[摩蘇爾|摩蘇爾]]居民說，武裝分子警告他們不可使用這个名稱，否則會割去他們的舌頭<ref name="daeshstar">{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/world/2014/09/12/what_to_call_militants_isis_isil_daesh_or_islamic_state.html|date=2014-09-12|publisher=Toronto Star|title=What to call militants: ISIS, ISIL, Daesh or Islamic State?|accessdate=2014-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915030844/http://www.thestar.com/news/world/2014/09/12/what_to_call_militants_isis_isil_daesh_or_islamic_state.html|archive-date=2014-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
